Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.87,0:00:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两个人的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.61,0:00:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是无法重叠在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小恋 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然这样下去是不行的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.73,0:02:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷 之后就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些家伙 想要逃掉值日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫逃掉 这本来就不是我们该做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说啊 别让我们把话挑明了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又想把活都推给天枷同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杏学姐也说过人对待事物经常是三分钟热度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于天枷的事 虽然我也想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们能做的 也只有静观动向而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说不要擅自行动 先静观其变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骚动过一段时间自然消失也不是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 之后一段时间内 天枷的事暂时由我负责
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,义之
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟启动了天枷的人是我 我必须承担责任才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 我估计会有一段时间不能来参加乐队的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解 如果有难处你可一定要跟我们说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,义之
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小 小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想帮天枷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小恋…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在就请交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢天枷的人 也会敌视她身边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想让小恋遇到危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,义之…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱内 美夏一个人能回家的 别担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把我当傻瓜 美夏我可是最尖端科技的结晶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们竟然把我当小孩看待…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 在这里在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 义之君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷同学也在呢 正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一个提议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提议？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷同学 这段时间 要不要成为我们家的一员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们家的一员？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这件事解决之前 让她一直在我们家住下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟还是小心一点的好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又让你费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是谢谢你的好意 还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 这可是校长命令哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样确实挺好的呢 对吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯… 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 就这么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定？ 就这么决定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 小恋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看搞笑Gong Show
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看歌曲Top10
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看搞笑Gong Show
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看歌曲Top10
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看搞笑Gong Show
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看歌曲Top10
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定看这个了吧 樱内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷 你在别人家就不知道客气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.28,0:06:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 你用不着这么说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 美夏可是因为校长一直唠叨个不停才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换言之便是客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥你就想这么随便地招呼客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们说的非常对 那么就请随意看你们喜欢的节目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱内 你挡着我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢天枷的人 也会敌视她身边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想让小恋遇到危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 便当？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我想让大家一起吃所以做了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷同学喜欢的香蕉三明治也有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不好意思呢 让你这么费心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 快来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷同学又…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 小恋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 没跟你在一起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月岛到底在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天没有社团活动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天休息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}From奈奈佳  知道小恋在哪里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不良少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也确实是想要休息了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有义之君的社团活动 就像是没有草莓的草莓蛋糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}To奈奈佳  就别去打扰她了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息的理由也并不是因为这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:08:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你昨天没去社团活动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈奈佳发短信给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 是因为我的原因吧 昨天…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为昨天不在状态
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以怕奈奈佳说我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在状态？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 别担心 我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 了解了 要我去跟涉也说一声吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没事 我会跟他说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:09:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小恋…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候才能给我个答复
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷美夏那件事 再怎么谨慎认真也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也回应的太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也解决不了问题 我就用我的方式来做出回应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会向PTA和教育委员会提出异议
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}PTA：家长教师会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直这么含糊搪塞可不是办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音姬 你真的不知情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音姬 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真由纪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真由纪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷同学她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,博士最后…了却了自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泽井同学 因为机器人才让家庭支离破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还被夺去了自己的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一直是这样认为的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 天枷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,台湾香蕉和厄瓜多尔香蕉 要哪种
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱内 随便哪个都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪一个香蕉素比较多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然连学生会那边都串通过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊 我没有啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别装傻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管樱内你做什么 我都绝对不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器人 机器人我绝对不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等一下 不是你接不接受的问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样 很了解班长的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不全是机器人的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底了解什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种人到底能了解什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然之间就失去了父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直伤心 痛苦着 什么办法也想不出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能一直这么哭 你怎能体会我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班长…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.53,0:14:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器人把我的一切都夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也因为这个 我 我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛奶找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:15:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 谢谢你了 勇斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 你们是姐姐的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 我叫泽井勇斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是懂礼貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我们走吧 勇斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是第一次知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班长有那么小的一个弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泽井会生气也是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家里还有个这么大的孩子呢 现在被机器人搞得一团糟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生气也是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那些事和天枷一点关系都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美夏至今为止没有相信过任何一个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以说是憎恨人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类只顾自己方便制造出了机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果妨碍自己的生活 马上就毫不犹豫地废弃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直相信人类很险恶 机器人总是扮演着被害者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 我犯了一个非常大的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有因机器人而遭到不幸的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像泽井那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美夏是机器人 泽井是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但泽井和以前的美夏是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:16:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,资本主义经济的发展使社会的构成变得更为复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}当经济处于衰退时期 就业者数量下降 收入的减少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}在这不容乐观的形势下 个人收入的变化量也无法与之同步…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷虽然是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 还是得想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}至此 有分析指出这个问题必须由社会与国家相结合来进行解决
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}也就诞生了社会保障问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}日后 社会保障制度…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈奈佳？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}From奈奈佳  看外面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来是没问题了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多吃些 多吃些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天枷同学的事能平安解决就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.10,0:18:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小恋 看你一脸寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得义之做得很对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…那个…寂寞什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是瞒不过奈奈佳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是义之君啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去开门哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小恋？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈奈佳 那个 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得义之为了天枷同学这么努力是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真心这么想的 但是 正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不希望义之为我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,义之为我操心 虽然很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但并不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也希望可以帮义之一把
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.99,0:20:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和义之一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是恋人 我想两个人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我却隐藏着自己真正的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至还撒了「不想让义之为难」 这样的谎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直这么压抑着自己 一直挑义之爱听的话说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样根本就不是我 不是真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和义之交往以前 还没有这种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关系本应比青梅竹马更进了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这么痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在和义之在一起好痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 我会讨厌自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会开始讨厌义之的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小恋 很难受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也许已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,388)}嘴里叼着面包说着迟到了迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.45,0:23:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,388)}在拐角撞到的人是转学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.29,0:23:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,388)}遇到这种女生的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,388)}会说神啊 这种事还真是难碰上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,388)}嗯？倒不是说多讨厌…
